## Project Insights
•	Fruits are the top-performing product category.
•	Sub-Saharan Africa and Europe generate the highest profit.
•	Offline sales slightly outperform online sales in quantity.
•	Sales show fluctuations across years with peak performance in mid-years.
•	High and medium order quantities dominate the distribution.

## Final Conclusion
The dashboard effectively highlights key business metrics and trends, enabling better understanding of sales performance. It helps identify high-performing regions and products while also revealing opportunities for improvement in underperforming areas. This project showcases the power of Excel in transforming raw data into meaningful business insights.
